citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
* A facility representative was not available on 1/22/16 at 1:15 PM to do a facility inspection.
* Inspector knocked on the front door of the licensees cattery. Inspector called telephone number given by the
licensee. Inspector waited required 30 minute time for licensee to show up.
* Copy of inspection report was sent by regular mail.

ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
*  A facility representative was not available on 1/22/16 at  1:15 PM to do a facility inspection.
*  Inspector knocked on the front door of the licensees cattery.  Inspector called telephone number given by the
licensee.  Inspector waited required 30 minute time for licensee to show up.  
*  Copy of inspection report was sent by regular mail.
